ssets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家係滿電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc582104359e0359abff5dcd2e174259634ba69e","tid":495091,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T12:50:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>充到50%最好<br />\n<br />\n太低會死<br />\n100%會縮缸</blockquote><br />\n白癡鋰電長期滿電會冇咁快死</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁應該點樣放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真心求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家係滿電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔先理佢有幾多電<br />\n就仲放係度唔會出事"},{"pid":"885faebf6264ca44f981ec9b7dd36ee4d141495e","tid":495091,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T12:50:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>充到50%最好<br />\n<br />\n太低會死<br />\n100%會縮缸</blockquote><br />\n白癡鋰電長期滿電會冇咁快死</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁應該點樣放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真心求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家係滿電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔<span style=\"color: red;\">洗</span>理佢有幾多電<br />\n就仲放係度唔會出事</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b5ca30ee3f072bb65423074f8a6b6dec2bd9d41a","tid":495091,"uid":2373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T12:51:32.000Z","msg":"長放的話5~60%左右就最好"},{"pid":"e089cd7f5f2c37e055cb7cc170df1700dc8da962","tid":495091,"uid":6366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T13:09:12.000Z","msg":"其實好多電子產品說明書有寫<br />\n每半年充滿一次 然後繼續放就得<br />\n<br />\n你放會走電 電壓低過某個位就差唔返<br />\n所以差滿去放"},{"pid":"aa79cd95466028aa2e7e41ff528ea388d6363810","tid":495091,"uid":89182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T13:29:09.000Z","msg":"唔好低過20%<br />\n<br />\n唔好充過90%<br />\n<br />\n會耐用好多"},{"pid":"6c8d6d87cb0e343c361e303dce42bfabd957c469","tid":495091,"uid":15567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T14:55:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>充到50%最好<br />\n<br />\n太低會死<br />\n100%會縮缸</blockquote><br />\n白癡鋰電長期滿電會冇咁快死</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.asus.com/hk/support/FAQ/1009546/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asus.com%2Fhk%2Fsupport%2FFAQ%2F1009546%2F&d=0SiDj62cuN3EJFKh3J%2F8Kozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=ab6bf579\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.asus.com/hk/support/FAQ/1009546/</a><br />\n華碩教嘅電池保養自己睇啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6. 若手機、平板電腦或電池組長時間靜置未使用，請不要對電池進行完全充電或完全放電，建議每二個月將裝置充電到約 60% 再進行存放。<br />\n7. 如果電池在沒電的情況下存放，電池會進入過度放電狀態，有機率性造成沒辦法再充電使用的情形。如果電池在充滿電的情況下存放，有機率性會損失部分電池蓄電力，導致電池使用時間縮短。<br />\n8. 裝置在長期存放之後，再次開機使用前，建議先使用華碩原廠隨附的變壓器充電兩小時以上。"},{"pid":"7c1b20544d0d74724da141e2123d4651680d8ce5","tid":495091,"uid":82970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T15:30:57.000Z","msg":"網上好撚多教柒人，呃鳩你放電<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你老母，特別是新電特別敏感，我新買laptop一放電太低就低左1%壽命，新買一個月內得返93%之後冇跌過，依家2年，都冇再跌過，經常帶返學用，但保持長期有電其實好難降壽命。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f5fc49295ab8e1c583e99571ddee020705e5dd","tid":495091,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T18:29:42.000Z","msg":"放3-40 % is what I do<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d542a9e012cdcc30282ba670a6af90d0a0ff7d6","tid":495091,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T19:15:17.000Z","msg":"60%"}]}